Package: basicMLforLSCM
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Machine Learning Workflow for Logistics and Supply Chain Management
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Vince", "Castillo", email = "castillo.230@osu.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An interactive, teaching-oriented R package that guides students through
    the 5-step supervised machine learning regression workflow using linear regression.
    Designed for BUSML 4382 at The Ohio State University. Students make analytical
    decisions at each step via console menus while the package handles the R code.
